---

<div class="container">
    <div class="tablet:min-h-[28.75rem] desktop:min-h-[32.9375rem]">
        <p class="text-subtitle mobile:mb-[1.3125rem] desktop:mb-[0.5625rem]">Tech</p>

        <div class="relative mb-[1.875rem] tablet:mb-[1.875rem] desktop:mb-[15.625rem]">
