            <p class="text-regular hidden desktop:block desktop:absolute desktop:top-[9.75rem] desktop:left-[44.8125rem] desktop:max-w-[34.375rem]">Dodo IS, our own cloud-based tech platform covers everything from ordering to delivery, production and <span>data-driven chain management<span>.</p>
